description: AMUNDI MSCI EUROPE MOMENTUM FACTOR UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the MSCI Europe Momentum Index, whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to easily follow in a single transaction the best performance during the last 6 and 12 months of an equity momentum strategy, before the last index rebalancing date, by emphasizing large and mid-cap stocks across 15 Developed Markets countries in Europe with high price momentum, while maintaining reasonably high trading liquidity, investment capacity and moderate index turnover. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi MSCI Europe Momentum Factor UCITS ETF - EUR (C)
